Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.82,1:44:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,where did all my\Nthat's all my education of history
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.82,1:44:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because\Nas a child I slept through history
