Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.05,1:45:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway so\Nthe evolution of our planet Earth
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.11,1:45:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and our planetary system then\Nthis spinning lava
