Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.21,1:45:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,emerges as life\Nso all life is of divine origin
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.56,1:45:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the physical mechanical world\Nis of a different order of existence
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.56,1:45:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,this order cannot create\Nthis order
