Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.88,1:45:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot jump level\Nthis level cannot cause this level
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.23,1:45:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it takes\Nthe energy of divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.84,1:45:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,interacting with matter\Nso matter interacting with matter
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.22,1:46:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is incapable of creating life\Nthat's a true statement of the Lord
