Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.98,1:46:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is incapable of producing life\Nbecause life is of a completely different order
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.98,1:46:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,high level of\Nabstraction
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.98,1:46:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a completely different paradigm\Nwith different qualities
