Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.64,1:46:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is still not infinite\Nno it takes the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.64,1:46:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,an infinite omnipotence\Nout of which arises life
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.64,1:46:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and its interaction with matter\Nwhen divinity looks at matter
