Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.88,1:46:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,okay\Nso life then emerges as creation
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.11,1:47:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that's good to know\Nbecause if life is an aspect of divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.11,1:47:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,then it can't be extinguished\Ncannot be extinguished
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.11,1:47:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so we have another addition to man's knowledge\Nwe have the survival of matter
