Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.61,1:47:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the indestructibility of life itself\Nthus we're reaffirmed just again
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.61,1:47:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not using kinesiology\Nexcept to just affirm the reality of what is obvious
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.88,1:47:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what's obvious\Nokay
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.88,1:47:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what's obvious is that life is indistinguishable\Nand that death is not a possibility
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.88,1:47:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,resist\Nyes
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.88,1:47:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for death to be a possibility\NGod would have to be subject to mortality
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.55,1:47:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand that?\Nyeah
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.55,1:47:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,okay\Nso you see electricity
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.39,1:47:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is independent of this toaster\Nand this cooking machine
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.39,1:47:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and this egg beater\Nand this washing machine
