Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.92,1:48:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,electricity\Nso does the toaster
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.92,1:48:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the washing machine says\NI'm the source of electricity
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.92,1:48:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,now you're the locus\Nyou see
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.48,1:48:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so the source of life is like the electricity\Nand you're plugged into it
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.48,1:48:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but you cannot extinguish electricity\Nso life is not linear
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.48,1:48:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore it cannot go on and off\Non-ness and off-ness
