Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.56,1:49:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is doing it on its own\Nit's not a you witnessing
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.27,1:49:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just witnessing witnessing\Nit's autonomous
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.27,1:49:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,witnessing is autonomous\Nit's an aspect of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.27,1:49:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't need a personal you\Nit only needs a personal you to report it
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.27,1:49:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,as a person\Nsubjective experience to report it
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.18,1:49:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the witnessing then becomes more abstract\Nand moves into consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.18,1:49:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the realization that consciousness is also beyond volition\Nthe consciousness is autonomous happening of its own
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.22,1:49:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it is what it is\Ncomplete and total
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.40,1:50:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so the realization then eventually comes\Nand it opens up into realization
