Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.60,1:50:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that in and of myself\NI am complete and total and need nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.97,1:50:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in and of myself oh lord\NI am complete and total and need nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.97,1:50:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a statement of the absolute truth\Nresist
