Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.48,1:50:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the less you need\Nyou don't really need anything
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.72,1:50:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,they're conveniences\Nthey're conveniences
